bilingual.source: Can you help me wrap the gift wrapper?
bilingual.target: 你能帮我把礼物的封皮包好吗？

bilingual.source: You can use this wrapper to wrap a gift.
bilingual.target: 你可以用这个包皮来包礼物。

bilingual.source: Please cover the leftovers with plastic wrap.
bilingual.target: 请用保鲜膜把剩菜包起来。

bilingual.source: You can recycle old newspapers to wrap gifts.
bilingual.target: 你可以再利用旧报纸来包礼物。

bilingual.source: I need some tape to wrap the gift.
bilingual.target: 我需要一些胶带来包装礼物。

bilingual.source: I like to wrap my sushi with nori.
bilingual.target: 我喜欢用紫菜包裹我的寿司。

bilingual.source: She covered the cake with plastic wrap.
bilingual.target: 她用保鲜膜包住了蛋糕。

bilingual.source: I need some Sellotape to wrap this gift.
bilingual.target: 我需要一些透明胶带来包装这个礼物。

bilingual.source: Wrap the cables neatly to avoid tangling.
bilingual.target: 整齐地包裹电缆以避免缠绕。

list.abstract: WRAP是由四个英文字的缩写结合而来。原文是WORLDWIDE RESPONSIBLE ACCREDITED PRODUCTION,中文译意是「负责任的全球成衣制造」。环球服装生产社会责任原则是参与WRAP认证项目生产设施的核心标准。该项目的是独立监控和证明制造业符合这些全球性的社会责任标准，并保证产品是在合法、人性化和符合伦理的条件下生产的。WRAP 认证项目坚信以工厂为基础的认证，是保证工作场所符合WRAP生产原则的最有效方法。WRAP项目将改善工作场所条件的首要责任放在拥有和经营缝制产品制造设施的业主身上。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, come on. Saran Wrap on the toilet seat, you don't think that's just a little funny?
yingyinNormal.zh: 马桶包了保鲜膜，那没有一点点好笑吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You want me to wrap it? No, it's okay. I'm gonna stab my friend in the chest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要包起来吗？不用了，我要用它直刺我朋友胸口。

yingyinNormal.en: Sure you do. I can tell by the wrap job. She can't make corners like this, Manny!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你肯定知道，一看就知道礼物是谁包的，她折不出这样的角，曼尼！

yingyinNormal.en: Will you join us, Mr. Gatsby? Two bottles of whiskey. Wrap them in a towel. Come on, Nick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 盖茨比先生，你也来吗？两瓶威士忌，用毛巾包好，尼克，走啊。

yingyinNormal.en: That's right. That's right. Saran Wrap on the toilet seat so the pee goes everywhere. Oh that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，是的，马桶座上包了保鲜膜，于是尿尿时喷得到处都是。哦，那个啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got wine at my place and some bubble wrap we could pop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我家有酒，我们还可以摁泡泡塑料包装。

yingyinNormal.en: You see the disk in front and then when it goes around you see the disk wrap up around the top of the black hole and wrap around the bottom of the black hole.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看到前面的吸积盘，然后当它绕着，你会看到吸积盘绕着黑洞顶部包裹，然后绕着黑洞底部弯曲。

yingyinNormal.en: I suppose I could wrap up an order of Mee krob and a couple of lottery scratchers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看我能打包一份脆炸米粉再加一些刮奖券。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you making him a sandwich? No it's, more like a wrap. Okay so, I'm gonna go guys. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在替他做三明治吗？不，比较像包装纸。好，我要走了。

yingyinNormal.en: This is unbelievable. I have never been so insulted in my life. Now, if you'll wrap up my free crab cakes, I'll be on my way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太离谱了，我从未被如此羞辱过。现在如果你帮我把蟹肉饼打包，我就马上离开。

yingyinNormal.en: Only because she's always in such a hurry. Is life so busy you can't take 20 minutes to get out the straight-edge and wrap a gift anymore?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那只是因为她总是匆匆忙忙的，生活真有这么忙碌吗？连抽出20分钟找一把直尺好好包装礼物的时间都没有吗？

yingyinNormal.en: OK, we've got dough ready. Just take off this wrap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在面团做好了，揭下保鲜膜。

yingyinNormal.en: Nobody cares, Hofstadter. Wrap it up. Right. To Howard. To Howard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人想听，霍夫斯塔德，总结陈词吧。好吧，敬霍华德。敬霍华德。

yingyinNormal.en: Next, a wheat starch skin, the translucent dumpling wrap. Just rolling it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 接着是小麦淀粉外皮，半透明的饺子皮。就这么一直搓。

yingyinNormal.en: The moment you step foot off that plane, it's a wrap. You're not coming back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布莱恩你一下飞机就完蛋了，你可能回不来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I could get into the head wrap but the veil across the mouth, it freaks me out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 头巾我还能接受。但是嘴前的面纱看着就诡异。

yingyinNormal.en: Firefly did a movie to wrap things up. Buffy the Vampire Slayer continued on as a comic book.
yingyinNormal.zh: 《萤火虫》出了电影版来收尾，《吸血鬼猎人巴菲》以漫画继续延伸了下去。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy! Can we go and play in the snow? Yes, but it's very cold outside, so you must wrap up warm. Hurray!
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，我们可以去外面玩雪吗？可以，但是外面非常得寒冷。所以你们必须多穿点。好嘞！

yingyinNormal.en: We wrap it round and round like this. It's a bit bumpy. No, I smooth the jolt with my hands and I add a handle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 接下来我们把黏土像这样叠起来。可是这样就不平整了吗。接下来我用手把表面抹平然后再加上个一个手把。

yingyinNormal.en: What we want to do is just slice long thin strips like this. Wrap one Chinese cabbage leaf around each meatball.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们只需要切开像这样切成细长条，在每个肉丸边放一片大白菜叶。
